Scenario: Customer determines the quantity of the product to be purchased. (Success Case)
"Given that I am a customer of the website
And I want to determine the quantity of a product to be purchased
When I open the product page
And I press on "-" button
Then I should see the product's quantity decreased by one 
Or I press on "+" button
Then I should see the product's quantity increased by one."


Scenario: Customer determines the quantity of the product to be purchased. (Failure Case)
"Given that I am a customer of the website
And I want to determine the quantity of a product to be purchased
When I open the product page
And I press on "-" button
And The current quantity is 1
Then I should see the product's quantity at 1 not decreasing any more". 

